text: Unforgettable Blast () is a 2015 Chinese comedy film directed by Yan Tinglu. It was released in China on May 22, 2015. ==Cast== *Jiang Chao *Jiang Xueming *Wang Xia *Yang Qing *Luo Jia *Jiang Yihong *Lei Di ==Reception== By May 23, 2015, the film had earned at the Chinese box office. ==References== Category:2015 comedy films Category:Chinese comedy films Category:Chinese films
